    <h4>For my next trick...</h4>
    <p>I want to get some LEDs connected to this device and control them from here. Currently I have what I believe is a WS2812 (NeoPixel). There are 17 on the strip and I believe I can power them from the PI without any other external power source. Below are some resources to help get me started.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.adafruit.com/product/1376?length=1">The NeoPixel strip lights</a>
